00:38:47.520 --> 00:38:52.920 align:middle line:90%


00:38:52.920 --> 00:38:54.990 align:middle line:84%
The pyramid seems to
have been positioned here

00:38:54.990 --> 00:38:57.790 align:middle line:84%
with the explicit purpose
of marking the site.

00:38:57.790 --> 00:39:00.145 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:39:00.145 --> 00:39:03.520 align:middle line:90%


00:39:03.520 --> 00:39:06.150 align:middle line:84%
The tunnel and the
pyramid on top of it

00:39:06.150 --> 00:39:09.030 align:middle line:84%
both lined up with a
significant astronomical event

00:39:09.030 --> 00:39:16.820 align:middle line:84%
when the pyramid was built
just over 2,000 years ago.

00:39:16.820 --> 00:39:19.200 align:middle line:84%
