line just after sunset.

00:39:26.550 --> 00:39:30.200 align:middle line:90%


00:39:30.200 --> 00:39:33.690 align:middle line:84%
This only happened twice a year,
when the sun had been directly

00:39:33.690 --> 00:39:35.718 align:middle line:90%
overhead.

00:39:35.718 --> 00:39:39.110 align:middle line:84%
To face these stars head
on, the Pyramid of the Sun

00:39:39.110 --> 00:39:42.710 align:middle line:84%
and the whole axis of the city
