00:39:42.710 --> 00:39:44.470 align:middle line:90%
by 15 and a half degrees.

00:39:44.470 --> 00:39:51.805 align:middle line:90%


00:39:51.805 --> 00:39:54.010 align:middle line:84%
The sites astronomical
alignments

00:39:54.010 --> 00:39:56.020 align:middle line:84%
