00:41:32.890 --> 00:41:33.690 align:middle line:90%


00:41:33.690 --> 00:41:36.740 align:middle line:84%
>> Harleston's surveys have
been carried out with impeccable

00:41:36.740 --> 00:41:37.910 align:middle line:90%
professionalism.

00:41:37.910 --> 00:41:40.220 align:middle line:84%
