00:41:52.920 --> 00:41:54.270 align:middle line:90%
100,000 to one.

00:41:54.270 --> 00:41:56.580 align:middle line:84%
And that the side of
its main structure

00:41:56.580 --> 00:41:58.338 align:middle line:84%
represents the
radius of the Earth.

00:41:58.338 --> 00:42:00.970 align:middle line:90%


00:42:00.970 --> 00:42:02.920 align:middle line:84%
