00:42:46.570 --> 00:42:51.640 align:middle line:90%


00:42:51.640 --> 00:42:54.200 align:middle line:84%
>> What Harleston's saying is
that there are measurements

00:42:54.200 --> 00:42:56.360 align:middle line:84%
of time in the dimensions
of the building,

00:42:56.360 --> 00:42:59.750 align:middle line:84%
