proportional to the other.

00:43:06.650 --> 00:43:09.640 align:middle line:90%


00:43:09.640 --> 00:43:12.130 align:middle line:84%
This suggests a fantastically
sophisticated knowledge

00:43:12.130 --> 00:43:13.010 align:middle line:90%
on the builders.

00:43:13.010 --> 00:43:13.810 align:middle line:90%
>> It does.

00:43:13.810 --> 00:43:17.950 align:middle line:90%
It's high precision astronomy.

00:43:17.950 --> 00:43:21.380 align:middle line:10%
But the thing about this place
is, the space measurements

00:43:21.380 --> 00:43:24.590 align:middle line:10%
and the time measurements unify.

00:43:24.590 --> 00:43:28.460 align:middle line:84%
Once you know the basic
measure that repeats,

00:43:28.460 --> 00:43:29.930 align:middle line:90%
